# Spotify API Credentials
# Copy this file to .api_secrets and replace with your actual credentials
# To obtain your Spotify API credentials:
# 1. Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# 2. Log in with your Spotify account or create one if you don't have it
# 3. Click "Create an App" and fill in the required information
# 4. After creating the app, you'll see your Client ID and Client Secret
# 5. Click "Show Client Secret" to reveal your secret
# 6. Copy these values and replace the placeholders below

SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_spotify_client_secret_here